	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey guys,
<br />I'm starting some NES dev, and I want to make some EPROM cartridges I can mess around with on my CopyNES system. Trouble is, I use Linux.
<br />Does anyone know of a good EPROM burner that works in Linux? Preferably one that uses the serial port, as my parallel port will be in use by the CopyNES, and USB means you have to fight with drivers.

		

		</td>
