	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there any reason you want to use EPROM instead of Flash?  Re-using EPROMs is just a big PITA.  Especially if you have a CopyNES, you can do things the easy way with a devcart like the one I made (which is available).
<br />
<br /><a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=10682" class="postlink">http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=10682</a>
<br />
<br />I guess that doesn't help with the Linux thing.. but if you can already run the CopyNES host prog, you'd be pretty much set with FlashROM (and a custom cart).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
